'''Ferḥat Mhenni''', d aselway n Amusu [[Timanit n Tmurt n Iqbayliyen (MAK)|Timanit n Tmurt n Iqbayliyen (MAK)]], ilul-d deg 05 n Meɣres 1951 deg taddart n Illula, deg tama n temdinin n [[Buzegan|Buzegan]], [[Iɛezzugen|Iɛezzugen]], akk-d 
[[Aqbu|Aqbu]]. 


Asmi i d-kemmel almad-ines deg '''Tesdawit n Lezzayer''' (tamaneɣt) yebda-d tikli-ines di ccna deg 1973 imi yewwi tarrazt tamezwarut n tafaska tatrart n ccna n Lezzayer. 
Kra n lweqt mbeɛd isbeggen-d iman-is belli yella mgal anabad n iɣil n Lezzayer imi yebda-d abrid n tigwin; ɣef igiten agi yekcem-d ɣef lḥebs 13 iberdan.


[[Image:Acennay Ferḥat Mehenni.jpg|right|400px|thumb|'''Ferḥat Mehenni''']]

Mbeɛd [[Tafsut Taberkant|Tafsut Taberkant]], imi '''Tamselta n Lezzayer''' tenɣa yiwen weqcic amelsi yettusemman [[Masinisa Germaḥ|Masinisa Germaḥ]], Ferhat Mhenni isbed ''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''; tuddsa ixeddmen akken a tessiwed ar timanit n tmurt n leqbayel. Llan wid i qqaren belli ɣef demma n wannecta i yettwanɣa mmi-s [[Ameẓian Mhenni|Ameẓian Mhenni]] deg 2004.


'''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''' (''MAK''), [[Agraw n Yedles d Tugdut|Agraw n Yedles d Tugdut]] (''RCD''), akk-d [[Tirni Iɣallen Inemlayen|Tirni Iɣalen Inemlayen]] (''FFS'') d ikabaren isertiyen i sɛan ccan deg Tmurt n Izwawen.

